Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.64,0:00:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a soldier 而那也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.91,0:00:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.14,0:00:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同时站在火线的两端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.85,0:00:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕过危险的转角追过生与死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.26,0:00:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奔向前挑战谎言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.06,0:00:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论编织出多少谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.83,0:00:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相还是会照出光明的轮廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.88,0:00:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.44,0:00:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.01,0:00:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们的痛苦都抛在脑后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.28,0:00:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.92,0:00:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.55,0:01:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是士兵不是站着就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.96,0:01:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.52,0:01:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.09,0:01:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它们留给审判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.43,0:01:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.06,0:01:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.73,0:01:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲的时候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.47,0:01:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能奋起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.47,0:01:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻壳机动队 S.A.C. 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.35,0:01:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伪装成意外的他杀案件吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.26,0:01:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据调查员所述
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.82,0:01:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞的时候很可能故意对脑壳造成确实伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.53,0:01:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是卡车驾驶说他开车打瞌睡完全没有记忆?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.74,0:01:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为求慎重起见我们正在清查驾驶的电子脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.87,0:01:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  恐怕不会有任何发现吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.27,0:01:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜恐吓能源省犯人的线索就这样断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.85,0:02:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这个男人是单独犯的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.18,0:02:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害者的义体是丰田化工制2902型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.02,0:02:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑壳是Dermo制2706型改良版
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.32,0:02:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然型号落伍但两者都是全新的国产机种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.39,0:02:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表是市售的标准型式没有附加额外功能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有脸部是订制的高级品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.87,0:02:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  从细胞老化的程度来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.77,0:02:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是从第一次义体化就用到现在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.10,0:02:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以犯罪者来说这种换装模式不太正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.67,0:02:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上恐吓手法好像也很拙劣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.21,0:02:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能连能源省丑闻这个情报都只是故弄玄虚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.95,0:02:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他却在被逮捕的前一刻死在疑似暗杀的手法之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.99,0:02:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个印记是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.46,0:02:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是旧首都新宿区的标志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.80,0:02:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大战中沉入水底?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.40,0:02:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个脑壳不知为何镀了一层玻璃和铅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.50,0:02:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是镀的时候刻上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.91,0:03:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是男子身上的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.08,0:03:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有一个记者的联络方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.41,0:03:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以当作清查身分的线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.68,0:03:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该是结婚戒指吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.29,0:03:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#06 潜在热源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.70,0:03:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们事务所的确有接到希望见面的联络电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.34,0:03:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.17,0:03:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然密告的内容十分可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.07,0:03:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  电话好像是从东京的公用终端机打来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.68,0:03:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.61,0:03:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么密告的内容是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.48,0:03:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟能源省有关的丑闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.88,0:03:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是一一确认这种密告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.39,0:03:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不就什么事都做不了了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.02,0:03:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很少跟他实际碰面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.96,0:03:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  他说要寄给我能够证明这条新闻的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.10,0:03:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是两位吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.66,0:03:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位抽不抽烟呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请往这边走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑漆漆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.01,0:04:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是什么能当证据的照片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜完全曝光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.85,0:04:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他大概是认为数位资料没有证据能力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.15,0:04:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在很少人会使用底片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.39,0:04:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个可以交给我保管吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.89,0:04:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊不过真的什么都没拍到喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.63,0:04:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子这个男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.46,0:04:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到被杀的前几天为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像都待在东京市内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.93,0:04:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还从那边把曝光的底片寄给记者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.97,0:04:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.87,0:04:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就根据这条线索到东京去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.11,0:04:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段期间我们会把他使用的终端机找出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.48,0:04:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一个人去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.55,0:04:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人都还在继续执行总理的贴身警卫工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我派一台塔奇克马跟你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.22,0:04:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辐射方面已经没问题了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.62,0:04:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为大战已经过去几年了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散布“日本的奇迹”之后（一种能清除辐射的微机械）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有再发现过残留辐射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.66,0:05:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.64,0:05:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新东京  新东京到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.28,0:05:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在到站的列车是往Berutarube的择捉3号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.59,0:06:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这么在意残留辐射我建议你去做义体化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不知不觉就觉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得不舒服吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我可以让你坐进驾驶舱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可能会让我晕车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少喽嗦  静静跟着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你这话是什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里打的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有见过这个男的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不认识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.41,0:07:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该是在这附近换新义体的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.48,0:07:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近几乎都是以最低限度机能刻苦生活的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.59,0:07:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给我看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.09,0:07:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近很多人失踪  说不定我认识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这家伙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.77,0:07:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识他吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认识这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.77,0:07:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  四、五天前有个在这种大热天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.67,0:07:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还穿黑西装的男人问过我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.41,0:07:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着危险面孔的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.01,0:07:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且刚刚在人群附近有个年轻小姐也在找同一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.62,0:07:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个帅哥到底干了什么好事啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.82,0:07:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.36,0:07:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.50,0:07:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问你们认识一个叫作古潭完治的人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.00,0:07:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.64,0:07:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.52,0:08:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种意外的宝贝果然很少见啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.26,0:08:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托古萨先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.27,0:08:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.83,0:09:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想挨揍就快滚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.41,0:09:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.65,0:09:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于联络时提到的男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.65,0:09:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已确认在关东招慰难民居住区的确有个男的叫古潭完治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.36,0:09:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.39,0:09:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把男子的照片和戒指给暂且纳入我保护下的女子看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.40,0:09:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说是古潭的东西没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.44,0:09:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女子是什么人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浅木琉璃子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.47,0:09:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年前曾参加援助难民的NG0(非政府组织)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.41,0:09:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那时候认识了古潭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.01,0:09:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来两人仍继续联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.85,0:09:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至约好有一天要在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.15,0:09:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  三个月前古潭失去联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.12,0:10:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在一个礼拜前突然收到表示要分手的信件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.33,0:10:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是她为了找古潭从秋田来到东京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.40,0:10:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.30,0:10:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续跟那个女人询问经过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.50,0:10:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.59,0:10:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古潭 to 琉璃子 forever
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.13,0:10:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古潭已经死了  对吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.80,0:10:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是古潭送我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.40,0:10:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说很快就能离开难民街了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.54,0:10:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是想去取得ID的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.58,0:10:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古潭的义体却通不过审查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.11,0:10:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他没有具备最低限度的性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.08,0:11:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道这件事之后  古潭他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.85,0:11:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始躲避我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.76,0:11:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是因为他认为我隐瞒了规格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.66,0:11:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没办法跟他联络上吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联络过好几次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.00,0:11:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还说要帮他取得新的义体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.64,0:11:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  他拒绝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新滨被发现的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.44,0:11:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古潭已经换上了国产的义体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.01,0:11:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有听他说过吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.28,0:11:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  没听他说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.68,0:11:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.73,0:11:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说他在死前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.50,0:11:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涉嫌恐吓某个国家机关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.40,0:11:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要勒索金钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.53,0:11:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听你说这件事的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.14,0:11:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为古潭是为了得到义体才想到要去恐吓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.31,0:11:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果他早就更换过义体了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.11,0:11:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在得到义体之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.71,0:12:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还要去犯下恐吓案件呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.12,0:12:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古潭虽然被迫过着怀才不遇的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.39,0:12:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  他不是那种会去犯罪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.99,0:12:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  古潭的死不是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.86,0:12:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是被某个人杀死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.66,0:12:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,减少跟你联络的那三个月当中他身上一定发生了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.94,0:12:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天去人多的地方打听看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.32,0:12:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是一个月前吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.12,0:12:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛传有个家伙在大量招用完全义体的劳工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.56,0:12:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说只要有意愿到“内环七”去工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.13,0:12:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就免费赠送不错的义体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.90,0:12:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免费?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.50,0:12:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个“内环七”是什么地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.10,0:12:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指没入水中的那一带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.60,0:13:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我没听说有人真的拿到义体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.08,0:13:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那说不定只是谣传罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.05,0:13:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人好像就拿到了新的义体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.05,0:13:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有没有人知道那个可以拿到义体的传言?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.99,0:13:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这个男子真的拿到全身义体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.03,0:13:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在还活着都是老师的功劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.02,0:13:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.52,0:13:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在内环七教了我很多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.99,0:13:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边发生了什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.96,0:13:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是按照指示工作而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.63,0:14:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得雇主是谁吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.10,0:14:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得叫什么黑松电设的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.00,0:14:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是要发掘在战争当中被掩埋的设备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要进入非常深的地底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.98,0:14:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要我们换成全身义体之后再集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.92,0:14:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于条件是义体化比率98％我一度想要放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.56,0:14:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来还是请黑市医生帮我谎报义体化比率混了进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些义体上有这个标志吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.27,0:14:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.54,0:14:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师对能够换装新义体感到非常高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.97,0:14:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己又没办法看到自己的脑壳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.98,0:14:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道是不是真的拿到新品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.08,0:14:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样召集到40个左右的工人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入非常深的地底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.96,0:15:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我之外好像也有人谎报了义体化比率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.39,0:15:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来我跟老师编成一组开始工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.80,0:15:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得他一直说什么“热交换管”之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.37,0:15:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然戴着防尘面具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是连鼻子里面都变黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.91,0:15:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师说只要切断感觉器官就没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.28,0:15:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我不是全身义体无法切断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.85,0:15:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果老师的表情变得非常可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.08,0:15:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说如果不马上离开这里我一定会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.52,0:15:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我无论如何都需要那笔钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没听老师的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.13,0:15:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是老师拿这个给我并且说要是这个变成黑色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.50,0:15:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要赶快逃出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.87,0:15:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在开工之后的第四天发生了严重的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然警报大作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.51,0:15:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里还在想出了什么事的时候从里面的工作现场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.11,0:15:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一群像是技术人员的人躺在担架上被抬了出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.78,0:16:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白这个工作有多危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.79,0:16:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此逃了出来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.99,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.83,0:16:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回过神来才发现有群身穿黑衣的人跑了进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.10,0:16:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和老师虽然顺利逃到外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.97,0:16:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  逃命过程中回头一看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.91,0:16:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现一起去的同伴都被关在巨大的铁门后面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后  古潭他怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.72,0:16:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说一定要把自己在隧道里看到的事情公诸于世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.92,0:16:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不知道去哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.93,0:16:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以带我们到内环七去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.17,0:16:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.37,0:16:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算给钱我也不回那种鬼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.34,0:16:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只带到半路也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.07,0:16:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.37,0:16:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想知道古潭在那里看到了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.12,0:17:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陆上自卫军已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.16,0:17:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我逃出来的时候还没有那道铁丝网
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.77,0:17:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里进去就能到同一个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.87,0:17:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我只能带到这里为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.34,0:17:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.14,0:17:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.39,0:18:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.57,0:18:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武装机甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.89,0:18:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跳过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  托古萨先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.11,0:20:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔奇克马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.70,0:21:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到站的列车是往新福冈的未来52号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.37,0:21:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古潭为了跟你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.57,0:21:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知有危险还是到那里去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.64,0:21:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚好又有足够知识知道那里是什么设施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会被杀害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.95,0:21:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回家一趟就去接古潭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.35,0:21:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事请马上跟我联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.92,0:21:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.13,0:21:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古潭在埋藏于深度地底的核电厂中碰到那件事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.27,0:21:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就以此事来恐吓能源省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.24,0:22:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 他这么做也有可能是想把这件丑闻公诸于世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.31,0:22:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.28,0:22:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据推测应该是在作业当中发生临界事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.02,0:22:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后急忙将其掩埋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.95,0:22:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军方好像也没有掌握到实际状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.76,0:22:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题在于想要挖出战前遗物的人到底隶属哪里管辖 有什么目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.43,0:22:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个穿黑西装的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.23,0:22:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这事还有内幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.70,0:22:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来之后马上汇整报告书给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.07,0:22:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.58,0:22:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(在现场发现的劳工)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.35,0:23:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出我体内行星和星星的银河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.96,0:23:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着它们每一个都唱着同样宁静的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.53,0:23:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在现实当中从来没看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.47,0:23:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的美丽事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.77,0:23:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有一点怀疑或恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.37,0:23:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到一个声音——醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.45,0:23:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字——然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.98,0:23:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我省视自身——醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.09,0:23:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到一道光随时都围绕着我——时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.25,0:23:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有真相  所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.83,0:23:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去让这一切成真的——它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.73,0:24:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在躯壳里的美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.00,0:24:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到一个声音——醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.01,0:24:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字——然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.67,0:24:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我省视自身——醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.68,0:24:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到一道光随时都围绕着我——时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.98,0:24:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有真相  所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.35,0:24:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去让这一切成真的——它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.52,0:24:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这个躯壳里
